parameters.name: Id
parameters.description: The ID of the multicast group.

parameters.name: LoRaWAN
parameters.description: The LoRaWAN information used with the multicast session. DlDr (integer) --- Downlink data rate. DlFreq (integer) --- Downlink frequency. SessionStartTime (datetime) --- Timestamp of when the multicast group session is to start. SessionTimeout (integer) --- How long before a multicast group session is to timeout. PingSlotPeriod (integer) --- The PingSlotPeriod value.

nested_params.name: SessionStartTime

nested_params.name: SessionTimeout
nested_params.description: How long before a multicast group session is to timeout.
